steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit003" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit003" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol003" Type "integer" for Table name "jit003"
Then I should see column with name "jitcol003" and index "4" of table name "jit003" has type "integer" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol003" Type "integer" for Table name "jit003"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox label "Column name" has value "Column name already exist"
When I close the modal popup
When I delete column Name "jitcol003" of table with Name "jit003"
Then I should NOT see column with name "jitcol003" and index "4" of table name "jit003" has type "integer" display
